---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-city"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4 trigo-positive-chapter"
                >La Ciudad</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6">La Ciudad Refugio</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#a8a29e] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="El trigo nos pidió quedarnos quietos. A cambio, nos dio muros."
                />
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div
                    class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-emerald-900/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">Jericó</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e]">
                            8000 a.C. - La primera ciudad amurallada
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-emerald-900/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15M5.25 3v18m13.5-18v18M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">Çatalhöyük</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e]">
                            7500 a.C. - 10,000 habitantes conviviendo
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-emerald-900/50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0012 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">Uruk</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e]">4000 a.C. - La primera metrópolis</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-base text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed pt-4">
                    Por primera vez, el ser humano no estaba a merced de la tormenta o la bestia.
                    Creamos espacios controlados, templados y seguros. La "casa" dejó de ser un
                    concepto temporal para convertirse en un legado.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-900/10 via-transparent to-transparent"
                >
                </div>

                <div class="relative w-full max-w-[320px]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-500/5 blur-3xl"></div>

                    <div
                        class="relative grid grid-cols-4 gap-3 p-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] rounded-2xl border border-emerald-900/30"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-800 to-stone-700 rounded-sm shadow-lg"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="h-24 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-800 to-stone-700 rounded-sm shadow-lg -mt-8"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="h-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-800 to-stone-700 rounded-sm shadow-lg -mt-4"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="h-28 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-800 to-stone-700 rounded-sm shadow-lg -mt-12"
                        >
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-700 to-stone-600 rounded-sm shadow-lg -mt-16 col-span-2"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="h-28 bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-700 to-stone-600 rounded-sm shadow-lg -mt-12 col-span-2"
                        >
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-t from-emerald-900/60 to-emerald-800/40 border-2 border-emerald-500/40 rounded-sm -mt-32 col-span-4 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_120%,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-500/20 via-transparent to-transparent"
                            >
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
                                <div
                                    class="w-3 h-3 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(52,211,153,0.5)]"
                                >
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 uppercase tracking-widest">
                                    Centro
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
